def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = []
    for i in range(n):
        a.append(list(map(int, input().split())))
    p = [0]*n
    p[0] = 1
    p[a[0][0]-1] = a[0][1]
    p[a[0][1]-1] = a[0][0]
    for i in range(1, n):
        if p[i] == 0:
            p[i] = a[i][0]
            p[a[i][0]-1] = a[i][1]
            p[a[i][1]-1] = a[i][0]
    print(*p)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
